name: Tezzy Everydays #5 | Cyclops Tezbot | May 11th, 2021
description: This is the fifth day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series.  I decided to go with a full on mini music video today featuring my original instrumental quickie "MIT". Of course Cyclops Tezbot is celebrating the fact that he's earned Tezos by selling free NFTs for .01 Tez on the secondary market. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
